@cjlortie Data analysis can be part of a DMP but a DMP covers a lot more than data analysis. What type of data, metadata? How much? Who will manage it? Where will it be stored? How will it be licensed? Who is responsible for it? How we people access it? ...
@cjlortie If non Arctic, not a good fit for the @Arcticdatactr. Look to the Knowledge Network for Biocomplexity (KNB) or @EDIgotdata as possible options
